r>Estimated play time is 1 to 2 hours per map, but don't worry! Supports up to 4x speed mode.<br>Let's aim for a high score!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745240/extras/a7136852083d4da8bc6cea9a978ba7b1.apng?t=1768360918\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745240/extras/a7136852083d4da8bc6cea9a978ba7b1.poster.avif?t=1768360918\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><strong><u>◆Complete single player ◆</u></strong><br>It's okay to interfere with other players, or to steel money or land!<br>You won't fight with friends!<br><br>※Please be careful※<br>KEMONO means a cute animal character.<br>It's not about \"KEMONO\" and Furry.<br>This is a board game in which animals become unit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745240/extras/72db377e03fb94e5f122ccd5630cee9a.poster.avif?t=1768360918\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745240/extras/72db377e03fb94e5f122ccd5630cee9a.webm?t=1768360918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745240/extras/72db377e03fb94e5f122ccd5630cee9a.mp4?t=1768360918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
